Class ArgumentRelativeVec2

java.lang.Object
net.minestom.server.command.builder.arguments.Argument<RelativeVec>
net.minestom.server.command.builder.arguments.relative.ArgumentRelativeVec2
public class ArgumentRelativeVec2 extends Argument<RelativeVec>
Represents a Vec with 2 floating numbers (x;z) which can take relative coordinates.

Example: -1.2 ~
